    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped out per MRL 2 factor matrix with documented justification. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all five operating points with GCI < 2% on primary QoI. The uncertainty quantification campaign (described in VR-01) confirmed that the acceptance conclusion is robust across the sampled parameter space. The model is judged sufficiently credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
